00:06:28,924 --> 00:06:31,887
to allow the players to reach higher viewpoints,

130
00:06:31,947 --> 00:06:35,451
which, you know, afford a much better view of the situation.

131
00:06:37,460 --> 00:06:39,721
And finally within the layer we have like you know a bunch of

132
00:06:39,821 --> 00:06:43,182
specific interactive objects that we had and that afford

