548
00:26:06,531 --> 00:26:09,152
the idea must be the more specific to your world

549
00:26:09,192 --> 00:26:11,794
that this idea is, like this particular game's world

550
00:26:11,834 --> 00:26:14,896
and not like all sci-fi games or all noir games or whatever,

551
00:26:15,496 --> 00:26:17,537
you know, the more you're building a particular thing

